      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "YTWEZ",
          "name": "tt",
          "fill": "#cdd6f4",
          "content": "节点 · Edge · 对话框 — 连接两节点即触发 Agent 对话，切换节点即切换对话历史",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "cv88H",
          "name": "su",
          "fill": "#a6adc8",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "任意方式引入新节点 → Edge 连接两个节点时弹出 Agent 对话（记录关联原因）→ 点击不同节点切换各自对话 → 新节点 Edge 旧节点时继承部分对话上下文",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
